item.title: Moon Tune - Southborne [House]

item.description:
Well done buddy. Nice calm feel with nice drive. Could do with a lot more progression I think. But it doesn’t have to be so “progressive”. I like how u drpped it towards the end for a final climax!

PS, I’m liking ur switch from melb bounce to house. I feel like we have done the same thing I’ve switched to progressive House. I guess we find our true passions
